---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="P1 Express">
    <h1 class="font-medium text-2xl mb-8 tracking-tighter">P1 Express</h1>
    <article class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert">
        <p class="text-xl font-medium text-neutral-500">
            The minimalist task management method.
        </p>

        <p>
            In a world of endless to-do lists and complex productivity systems,
            P1 Express offers a refreshing alternative: <strong
                >simplicity</strong
            >.
        </p>

        <h3>The Power of One</h3>
        <p>
            The core philosophy of P1 Express is built around focusing on what
            truly matters. It's not about managing more tasks; it's about
            managing the <em>right</em> task. By stripping away the noise, P1 Express
            helps you regain clarity and control over your day.
        </p>

        <div class="my-8 border-l-4 border-neutral-500 pl-4 italic">
            "Presented at the OMIMO Open Forum 2025"
        </div>

        <p>
            I had the privilege of presenting P1 Express at the recent <strong
                >OMIMO Open Forum 2025</strong
            >. The reception was incredible, validating the growing need for
            minimalist tools in our increasingly complex digital lives.
        </p>

        <h3>Get the App</h3>
        <p>Experience the method yourself with the P1 Express app.</p>

        <a
            href="https://www.p1express.app"
            target="_blank"
            class="no-underline block border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded p-4 hover:bg-neutral-100 dark:hover:bg-neutral-900 transition-colors"
        >
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-lg">p1express.app</span>
                    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 m-0">
                        Launch the web app
                    </p>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xl">â†—</span>
            </div>
        </a>

        <h3 class="mt-8">Learn More</h3>
        <p>
            Dive deeper into the methodology at the official OMIMO module page:
            <a href="https://omimo.org/en/modules/p1.express/" target="_blank"
                >omimo.org/en/modules/p1.express/</a
            >
        </p>
    </article>
</Layout>
